50|$|The Brain-Computer Interface {{system of}} Professor Jonathan Wolpaw aims to {{facilitate}} the communication of patients with <b>locked-in</b> <b>syndrome.</b> It enables patients to move a cursor on a computer screen, dictate a text or control a robotic arm.|$|E
